			<div class="breadcrumb">You are here: <a href="http://www.kidsumers.ca/" title="View Home">Home</a> / <a href="http://www.kidsumers.ca/category/product-review/" title="View all items in Product Reviews">Product Reviews</a> / <a href="http://www.kidsumers.ca/category/product-review/food/" title="View all items in Food">Food</a> / The Steak &#038; Baconator Sandwich</div>	<div class="post-6660 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-food tag-bacon tag-recipe tag-sandwich tag-steak">

				<h1 class="entry-title">The Steak &#038; Baconator Sandwich</h1>
		
		<div class="post-info"><span class="date published time" title="2011-08-12T10:36:33-0400">August 12, 2011</span>  By <span class="author vcard"><span class="fn"><a href="http://www.kidsumers.ca/author/kidsumers/" title="Posts by Sam" rel="author">Sam</a></span></span> <span class="post-comments"><a href="http://www.kidsumers.ca/2011/08/the-steak-baconator-sandwich/#comments">4 Comments</a></span> </div>		<div class="entry-content">
								
					<script type="text/javascript">
					//<![CDATA[
					nRelate.domain = "www.kidsumers.ca";
					//]]>
					</script><!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop --><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><div class='shareaholic-like-buttonset' style='float:right;height:30px;'><a class='shareaholic-googleplusone' shr_size='standard' shr_count='true' shr_href='http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kidsumers.ca%2F2011%2F08%2Fthe-steak-baconator-sandwich%2F'></a></div><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop --><div class="shr-publisher-6660"></div><p><strong><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-6676" style="margin: 15px;" title="Steak &amp; Baconator" src="http://www.kidsumers.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/2011aug551-300x161.jpg" alt="" width="210" height="113" /></strong></p>
<h3><strong>The Steak &amp; Baconator Sandwich Recipe</strong></h3>
<p>I recently took part in the <a title="Black &amp; Decker Ultimate Sandwich – Greek Wrap Zinger" href="http://www.kidsumers.ca/2011/08/black-decker-ultimate-sandwich-greek-wrap-zinger/" target="_blank">Black &amp; Decker Ultimate Sandwich Contest</a> through Mom Central Canada. My husband and I made a few sandwiches to test for the contest, and now that the contest is closed I thought it would be fun to share some of the other recipes we came up with. Today&#8217;s sandwich was created by Mike, and I called it the Steak &amp; Baconator!</p>
<p>Here are his ingredients (also listed below).</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6661" title="ingredients" src="http://www.kidsumers.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/2011aug37-517x359-custom.jpg" alt="" width="517" height="359" /></p>
<p>To start, you need the following:</p>
<ul>
<li>Italian bread (similar to sub bun size)</li>
<li>a 5 oz steak, grilled and sliced</li>
<li>Sliced tomato</li>
<li>1/4 cup chopped cucumber</li>
<li>A few leafs of lettuce</li>
<li>Havarti Cheese</li>
<li>Bacon</li>
<li>Diana Marinade Steak Spice</li>
<li>Club House Montreal Steak Spice</li>
<li>Basil Pesto</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6663" title="2011aug41" src="http://www.kidsumers.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/2011aug41-429x360-custom.jpg" alt="" width="429" height="360" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Step One:</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Marinate the steak in the Diana marinade for one hour. Mix Montreal steak spice to taste (about a teaspoon).</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6662" title="2011aug38" src="http://www.kidsumers.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/2011aug38.jpg" alt="" width="558" height="393" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Step Two:</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Butter and toast your bread.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6664" title="toasted bread" src="http://www.kidsumers.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/2011aug44-536x351-custom.jpg" alt="french bread" width="536" height="351" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Step Three:</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Lay the havarti cheese out on the bread.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6665" title="havarti cheese on bread" src="http://www.kidsumers.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/2011aug45.jpg" alt="Havarti cheese" width="419" height="336" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Step four:</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Put the lettuce and cucumber on top of the cheese.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6666" title="lettuce and cucumbers" src="http://www.kidsumers.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/2011aug46.jpg" alt="veggies" width="340" height="351" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Step five:</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Add tomato and pesto.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6667" title="tomatoes and pesto" src="http://www.kidsumers.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/2011aug48.jpg" alt="Pesto and tomato" width="662" height="406" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Step six:</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Place the heated steak on top of the tomato and pesto.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6668" title="Marinated steak" src="http://www.kidsumers.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/2011aug49-507x285-custom.jpg" alt="Steak on sandwich" width="507" height="285" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Step seven:</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Put the bacon on top of the steak.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6669" title="Put bacon on sandwich" src="http://www.kidsumers.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/2011aug51-547x229-custom.jpg" alt="Bacon" width="547" height="229" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Step eight:</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Broil the sandwich for about five minutes.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6670" title="Broil the sandwich" src="http://www.kidsumers.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/2011aug53.jpg" alt="Broil" width="480" height="360" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Your sandwich is finished! It looks and tastes great!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6671" title="Finished sandwich" src="http://www.kidsumers.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/2011aug55-494x265-custom.jpg" alt="steak and bacon sandwich" width="494" height="265" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6672" title="Lunch" src="http://www.kidsumers.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/2011aug63-443x338-custom.jpg" alt="sandwich" width="443" height="338" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">We had some family taste test our sandwiches and they couldn&#8217;t decide between this one and the Greek Wrap that I entered into the contest. They are both delicious, and even if we don&#8217;t win&#8230;we came up with some great new sandwich recipes!</p>
<p><!--more--><!-- BlogGlue Cache: No --></p>
