        <div id="user-profile-2" class="widget user-profile"><div class="widget-wrap"><h4 class="widgettitle">About Me</h4><p><span class="alignleft"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/41fea63698fcba93747cdbbaf9ce5f42?s=85&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kidsumers.ca%2Fwp-includes%2Fimages%2Fblank.gif&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-85 photo' height='85' width='85' /></span>I am Sheri, AKA Sam, the creator and author behind Kidsumers (a play on the word 'consumers').</p>
